      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, budget-friendly option for daily transportation. While it remains reliable for getting from A to B, please note there is visible wear on the interior upholstery and some minor scratches and dings on the exterior. The engine runs fine, though it may require some routine maintenance soon, such as a brake service or tire replacement, to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable car without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
