      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely breathtaking condition\u2014I\u2019ve honestly babied it since the day I brought it home! It looks and drives just like it did when it first rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and a spotless interior that still has that fresh feel. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
