    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable E46 M3, a purist\u2019s specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This unit boasts a flawless maintenance pedigree, including documented rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp, tactile shifts, paired with a perfectly calibrated M-Variable Differential Lock. The chassis retains its factory rigidity, supported by fresh bushings and a pristine suspension geometry. No VANOS rattle or oil consumption issues. This is a collector-grade example with zero deferred maintenance, offering a visceral, high-RPM experience that remains the benchmark for naturally aspirated performance.",
